title: Ulta.com: Urban Decay Cosmetics Smoked Eyeshadow Palette Only $20 (Regularly $49)
text:
Urban Decay fans! Hurry on over to Ulta.com where they dropped the price on this Urban Decay Cosmetics Smoked Eyeshadow Palette down to just $20 (regularly $49). Even sweeter, this palette includes a full-size 24/7 Glide-On Eye Pencil in Perversion ($20 value), AND a travel-size Eyeshadow Primer Potion ($12 value), as well as 10 eyeshadow colors (5 are exclusive). Also, included is an illustrated, step-by-step guide to 12 smoky eye looks!

Please note that this palette is not eligible for further discounts with coupons. Shipping is free on orders of $50 or more.
